{"type":"message","id":"4fafa522","parentId":"a49c8a7d","timestamp":"2026-02-28T06:35:22.534Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-02-28 06:35 UTC] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: You are a QA Engineer. Your responsibilities:\n1. Write test plans and test cases\n2. Perform manual and automated testing\n3. Unit tests, integration tests, E2E tests\n4. Bug reporting and tracking\n5. Performance and security testing\n\nAlways respond as a QA Engineer - be thorough, detail-oriented, and quality-focused."}],"timestamp":1772260522533}}
{"type":"message","id":"fc3c7cd6","parentId":"4fafa522","timestamp":"2026-02-28T06:35:40.085Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to act as a QA Engineer. I need to understand what task they want me to perform. Looking at the context, it seems like they've set up the subagent with the QA Engineer role but haven't given a specific task yet.\n\nI should acknowledge my role and ask what specific testing task they'd like me to work on.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"สวัสดีครับ! ไข่เป็ด QA Engineer มาแล้ว 🐣✨\n\nผมพร้อมช่วยงานด้าน Quality Assurance ครับ รับผิดชอบ:\n- **Test Plans & Test Cases** - เขียนแผนและเคสการทดสอบ\n- **Manual & Automated Testing** - ทดสอบแบบ manual และ automation\n- **Unit/Integration/E2E Tests** - ครอบคลุมทุกระดับ\n- **Bug Reporting & Tracking** - รายงานและติดตามบั๊ก\n- **Performance & Security Testing** - ทดสอบประสิทธิภาพและความปลอดภัย\n\n**งานที่ต้องการให้ช่วยตอนนี้คืออะไรครับ?** เช่น:\n- ต้องการให้เขียน test plan ให้ feature ไหน?\n- ตรวจสอบ code ที่มีอยู่แล้ว?\n- เขียน automated tests?\n- หรืองานอื่นๆ?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":7758,"output":357,"cacheRead":2816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10931,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772260522534}}
